messages.message:
is there a way to see aggregated customer feedback captured through the "Provide feedback on AI Hub form", versus seeing individual submissions? Ideally we'd be able to see the feedback per customer and then reconcile against any feedback we're hearing in customer conversations

https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C07BT7L5Q1M/p1724283351800549

Here's the feedback form responses in spreadsheet form: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Rv2nF9MRs7idraaB3uvEm-2YDwdIN6sEtFOs2bpXpTc/edit?gid=880915125#gid=880915125

You could make a new tab and do some parsing on the username or url to find just the responses you care about.

perfect! thanks so much!
